===Brand names===

A number of brand names include: Neurostil, Neurontin, Fanatrex, Gabarone, Gralise, Nupentin, Gabrion.<ref>http://thepharmaguide.com/content/view/5336/31/.</ref>

==Veterinary use==
Gabapentin is also used for some animal treatments, but formulations (especially liquid forms) for human use may contain the sweetener [[Xylitol]], which is toxic to dogs—so veterinary use of the human version requires caution.<ref>{{cite web |author=Barbara Forney |title=Gabapentin for Veterinary Use |url=http://www.wedgewoodpetrx.com/learning-center/professional-monographs/gabapentin-for-veterinary-use.html}}</ref>

